# This app has NO env vars at all — neither build-time (`$env/static/*`) nor
# runtime. There is no WhatsApp number in this repo: links go to
# wa.barrakudesbegur.org (the whatsapp-bot's index, a wa.me stand-in that
# accepts the same `?text=` param and resolves the number on its side). See
# src/lib/wa.ts.
#
# Local-only secrets/toggles (e.g. ADMIN_DEV for the /admin bypass) go in
# `.dev.vars`, not here. See docs/DEPLOY.md.
#
# The prefilled message is hardcoded in src/lib/wa.ts (WA_PREFILL) because it
# must exactly match the bot's flow trigger.
